UID:QkShuV1S6Dt4c4tAChRpO
SUMMARY:Cloud Room Coworking Open House Week
DTSTAMP:20260306T004541Z
DTSTART:20260306T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Curious about coworking and looking for the perfect spot to get
	 work done and reach your goals? Join us for a complimentary day during Op
	en House Week and experience what it’s like to be a part of our incredible
	 community!\n\nWhat's Included:\n\nFree Trial Day: Pick any day during Ope
	n House Week to try out our coworking space\, free of charge! Arrive anyti
	me 9am or later — whatever works best with your schedule.\n\nAccess to our
	 beautiful workspace including quiet desk space with monitors\, large loun
	ge area\, phone booths\, bar\, and outdoor patio.\n\nComplimentary coffee\
	, tea\, snacks and kombucha.\n\nHigh-speed Wi-Fi\, printing\, and meeting 
	rooms available for rent\n\nThe chance to meet like-minded professionals a
	nd get a feel for the Cloud Room vibe.\n\nSpecial Offer:\n\nIf you love yo
	ur free day with us and decide to become a member\, we’ll waive your initi
	ation fees when you sign up!\n\nHow to Join:\n\nReserve your free trial da
	y by selecting one day of your choice on our Calendly \\(one free trial da
	y per person\\)\n\nShow up and enjoy your day at Cloud Room! Be sure to ch
	eck in with the staff at the front of the lounge so we can give you a quic
	k tour of the space and get you set up with the wifi.\n\nSign up for membe
	rship to take advantage of waived initiation fees.\n\nDon’t miss this chan
	ce to test out our space\, meet amazing people\, and see if Cloud Room is 
	the perfect fit for your work needs!\n\nSpaces are limited—RSVP today.\n\n
	https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/cloud-room-coworking-open-ho
	use-week/18050488/2026-03-06T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/cloud-room-coworking-open
	-house-week/18050488/2026-03-06T00
