DESCRIPTION:Description "Werk the Jobsite" : Drag Queen BINGO Party!    Joi
	n the National Association for Women in Construction - Puget Sound Chapter
	\, Build with Pride Seattle\, and GSBA for an unforgettable Women in Const
	ruction Week celebration that brings community\, joy\, and visibility toge
	ther - with jobsite energy! Hosted at Stoup Brewing Capitol Hill\, Werk th
	e Jobsite: Drag Bingo & Party is a high-energy\, all-genders-welcome event
	 honoring the women\, femmes\, and allies who power the architecture\, eng
	ineering\, and construction \\(AEC\\) industry - and those helping redefin
	e what leadership and belonging look like within it. In the spirit of NAWI
	C's national Women in Construction Week theme\, this event celebrates prog
	ress while recognizing that building a stronger industry requires connecti
	on\, creativity\, and collective action. Expect drag bingo\, great drinks\
	, plenty of laughs\, and the chance to connect across organizations and id
	entities in a space that values authenticity and inclusion. Whether you're
	 swinging a hammer\, managing projects\, designing systems\, running a bus
	iness\, or advocating for change-this night is for you. Come celebrate. Co
	me connect. Come werk the jobsite.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/
	#/details/werk-the-jobsite-drag-queen-bingo-party/18234872/2026-03-06T00
